dc_title_s: Fence Boundary, Hopkins Marine Station, Pacific Grove, California, 1996
dc_description_s: This line shapefile represents ths fence boundary of Hopkins Marine Station, located near Monterey Bay in Pacific Grove, California. These data were digitized from USGS doqq NE_Monterey quadrangle (FILENAME: 36121E82) version 1996 12 at a 1:2,500 scale. This layer is part of a collection of data relating to Hopkins Marine Station located near Monterey Bay, California.These data are intended for researchers, students, policy makers, and the general public for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production.
